Education is the foundation of renaissance and the basis of national security. Our world today is swept by a tremendous scientific and technological revolution. In order to keep pace with the rapid and successive developments in various specific fields, the Faculty of Specific Education - Alexandria University - with its noble mission and the multiple roles and diverse tasks it performs, is the backbone in developing society and achieving its goals. The college strives to achieve quality and excellence and occupy a prestigious position on the map of higher education with its various academic curricula to provide students with technical and creative skills in all fields, aiming to prepare a qualified teacher educationally at the highest level of scientific competence, and to provide him with the skills and knowledge developed through the continuous development of programs and academic plans offered by the college in various specific specializations at the undergraduate and graduate levels to face all internal and external challenges necessary to break into the labor market, whether inside or outside the country, in addition to providing specialized research, training and consulting services to various community institutions in a way that contributes to community development.

I pray to God to grant us all success in achieving the college's mission and preparing teachers who believe in their mission and are capable of creativity and shaping a world of teaching, learning and competing in the labor market. My sincere prayers that our college reaches its rightful place and deserved position thanks to the efforts made by everyone. I also hope that what we provide in terms of information on this website of activities, conferences, seminars and workshops, as well as the achievements achieved by the college, which are constantly updated, achieves what you want to know, and we always strive for more continuous development of the website to meet your needs and desires in a way that achieves the public benefit.

With my sincere thanks and appreciation to everyone who contributed their efforts in preparing this website, and I pray to God Almighty to grant us all success in serving, elevating and developing our dear homeland;
